task.summary: Cleanup of project folder to support PyCharm and Git.
Transfered create vps view code from flask app
Added ram and bridge to model. Added additional view tests.
Added create_path and create_disk model and view.
Improved functional test for vps creation. Added logic for create disk and path checkboxes.
Worked out cleaner way of doing checkbox mapping.
Modified unittest to work with CHECKBOX_MAPPING directive. View now accepts 'on' and 'off' instead of True or False in line with form checkbox.
Added CreateUser view. Added ModifyVPS view.
Added disks and network devices to model
Created mock for backend rest call to vpssvr
